    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/j0rgbv-09/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_PRODUCT&editorId=608890156795036215&sectionId=608890156980437559)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"gg__kifShYw_text","label":"gg__kifShYw_text","default":"<span style=\"color:#17162E;\">Do You Still Have Any Doubts?</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5r67GKkA8_childItem_0","label":"gg5r67GKkA8_childItem_0","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Why this isn’t like the other self-tanners</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5r67GKkA8_childItem_1","label":"gg5r67GKkA8_childItem_1","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(239,240,241);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16px;\">How long does it last?</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5r67GKkA8_childItem_2","label":"gg5r67GKkA8_childItem_2","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(239,240,241);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16px;\">How many drops should I use?</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5r67GKkA8_childItem_3","label":"gg5r67GKkA8_childItem_3","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(239,240,241);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16px;\">How do I use it?</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5r67GKkA8_childItem_4","label":"gg5r67GKkA8_childItem_4","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(239,240,241);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16px;\">Is it good for sensitive skin?</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5r67GKkA8_childItem_5","label":"gg5r67GKkA8_childItem_5","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(239,240,241);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16px;\">Can I pay on delivery?</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKeQeBypCw_text","label":"ggKeQeBypCw_text","default":"<p>Most self-tanners are packed with alcohol, fake fragrance, and just DHA.<br>That’s why they dry your face out and turn you orange.</p><p>SerlinoLab is built different:</p><p><strong>No alcohol.</strong> Easy on sensitive skin.</p><p><strong>DHA + Erythrulose.</strong><br>DHA gives you the color.<br>Erythrulose makes it look real. Like you got sun — not sprayed in a booth.</p><p><strong>Italian carrot extract.</strong><br>Adds a warm, golden tone. Not that fake pumpkin shade.</p><p><strong>Sodium Hyaluronate + Aloe Vera.</strong><br>It doesn’t just give you color. It helps with dry skin while it’s working.</p><p><strong>End result?</strong><br>Natural tan. Better-looking skin.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggE2a9V-meS_text","label":"ggE2a9V-meS_text","default":"<p>3–4 days.<br>Even color.<br>Fades out slowly. No spots. No weird patches.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBr_m71saN_text","label":"ggBr_m71saN_text","default":"<p>Depends how dark you want to go.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Light — just a touch of color</strong><br>3–4 drops<br>Once every 3–4 days</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Medium — natural tan</strong><br>5–6 drops<br>Twice a week</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Darker — more noticeable</strong><br>7–8 drops<br>Three times a week</p><p>Start on the lower end.</p><p><br>You can always go darker next time.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg2xFSx-IzP_text","label":"gg2xFSx-IzP_text","default":"<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Wash your face with SerlinoLab Cleanser. Clean skin takes color better.</p><p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Put the drops in your palm. Rub evenly over face and neck in circular motions.</p><p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Wait 15–20 minutes before getting dressed.</p><p>Wash your hands right after.</p><p>For best results, exfoliate 24 hours before.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzn9yZbmxc_text","label":"ggzn9yZbmxc_text","default":"<p>Yes.</p><p>No alcohol.<br>Made with Aloe Vera, Sodium Hyaluronate, and Vitamin E to calm and support the skin.</p><p>Works great even after shaving.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gglFYYGZwgb_text","label":"gglFYYGZwgb_text","default":"<p>Yes.</p><p>You’ll get your order in 24–48 hours.<br>Pay cash when it shows up.</p>"}],
